snippet.title: HYPER//ECHO — TRAILER
snippet.description:
Launch(-ish) trailer for HYPER//ECHO, an experimental zone commissioned by ACMI, playable online as part of the virtual exhibition space Gallery 5.

PLAY NOW — https://hyperecho.acmi.net.au
HYPER//ECHO is accessible from 3 APRIL to 1 JULY.

Music — terminus by isyourguy
Full OST — https://firepitzone.bandcamp.com/album/hyper-echo-soundtrack
